            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This is surprising behavior but also (presumably) ancient. \n\nAs a first step, we could change it to throw an error, if a pattern resolves to empty. That may be all that's needed, and will also tell us how bad the fallout actually is.\n\nShould probably wait until after 0.12 release.",
